This project (PCL2-CE-CPP) is a C++ reimplementation of the Plain Craft Launcher 2 
Community Edition (PCL2-CE).

1. The source code of PCL2-CE-CPP itself is licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

2. This project is based on Plain Craft Launcher 2 Community Edition (PCL2-CE), 
   which is licensed under Apache License 2.0 by the PCL Community.
   
3. This project is a "Heavy Use" derivative work of Plain Craft Launcher 2 (PCL2).
   We strictly follow the "Plain Craft Launcher 2 Usage Guideline".
   We acknowledge the original author 龙腾猫跃 (LTCat) and retain the original guidelines.
   See "PLAIN CRAFT LAUNCHER 2 USAGE GUIDELINE".

